import {
  Accordion,
  AccordionDetails,
  AccordionSummary,
  Collapse,
  Grid,
  Typography,
} from "@material-ui/core";
import {
  AccountCircle,
  ExpandMore,
  HomeRounded,
  PhoneAndroidRounded,
} from "@material-ui/icons";
import FormSpacer from "components/FormSpacer";
import React from "react";
import InputCustomize from "./components/InputCustomize";
import SwitchCustomize from "./components/SwitchCustomize";

function ProfileForm(props) {
  const [checked, setChecked] = React.useState(false);
  return (
    <form>
      {/* <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid container item xs={6}>
          <InputCustomize
            title="Firstname"
            icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid container item xs={6}>
          <InputCustomize
            title="Lastname"
            icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      <FormSpacer />
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <InputCustomize
            title="Address"
            icon={() => <HomeRounded color="action" />}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <InputCustomize
            title="Email"
            icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
          <InputCustomize
            title="Phone"
            icon={() => <PhoneAndroidRounded color="action" />}
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      <FormSpacer /> */}

      <SwitchCustomize
        checked={checked}
        handleChange={(e) => setChecked(e.target.checked)}
      />

      <Collapse in={checked}>
        <InputCustomize
          title="Phone"
          icon={() => <PhoneAndroidRounded color="action" />}
        />
      </Collapse>

      <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary
          expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}
          aria-controls="panel1a-content"
          id="panel1a-header"
        >
          <Typography>Infomation</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Firstname"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Lastname"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Age"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </AccordionDetails>
      </Accordion>

      <FormSpacer />

      <Accordion>
        <AccordionSummary
          expandIcon={<ExpandMore />}
          aria-controls="panel1a-content"
          id="panel1a-header"
        >
          <Typography>Contact</Typography>
        </AccordionSummary>
        <AccordionDetails>
          <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Address"
                icon={() => <HomeRounded color="action" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Email"
                icon={() => <AccountCircle color="action" />}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid container item xs={12} sm={4}>
              <InputCustomize
                title="Phone"
                icon={() => <PhoneAndroidRounded color="action" />}
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </AccordionDetails>
      </Accordion>
    </form>
  );
}

export default ProfileForm;
